  "assertion": {
    "title": "Early exit on exact match cuts runtime 74% (1577s to 407s) while maintaining 50/50",
    "kind": "result",
    "statement": "Adding early termination in the restart loop when an exact match is found reduces total benchmark time from 1577s to 407s (74% speedup) while maintaining 50/50 exact matches. Reducing restarts from 5 to 3 or population from 600 to 400 loses 3 equations \u2014 6 equations require multiple restarts to solve reliably.",
    "claim": "supported"
  },
